Package importedImplementations.SanguptaBloom.bloomfilter.com.sangupta.murmur

package importedImplementations.SanguptaBloom.bloomfilter.com.sangupta.murmur
  • Class
    Description
    Murmur1
    A pure Java implementation of the Murmur 1 hashing algorithm as presented at Murmur Project Code is ported from original C++ source at MurmurHash.cpp
    Murmur2
    A pure Java implementation of the Murmur 2 hashing algorithm as presented at Murmur Project Code is ported from original C++ source at MurmurHash2.cpp and the 64-bit version at MurmurHash2_64.cpp
    Murmur3
    A pure Java implementation of the Murmur 3 hashing algorithm as presented at Murmur Project Code is ported from original C++ source at MurmurHash3.cpp
    MurmurConstants
    Simple constants for various masks to convert to unsigned values.
